{"tid":2479413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大BC省前法官：新疆「種族滅絕」是謊言","createTime":"2021-04-07T20:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T20:20:58.000Z","uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a17ac95d1ea78bc7d61ff9bb9e1ac0904c3d828","tid":2479413,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）由加拿大卑詩省省長賀謹（John Horgan）成立的華人社區諮詢委員會，成員之一前華人法官余宏榮（Bill Yee）接受當地電台訪問，他表示，加拿大政客對中國在新疆作種族滅絕的指控是捏造及謊言。當局回覆指，余宏榮只是表達個人意見，強調省政府支持加拿大聯邦政府的對華立場。<br />\n....<br />\n資料顯示，為卑詩省退休地區法官的余宏榮在廣州出生，1959年13歲時移民加拿大，先後任律師、市議員和法官，曾促成廣州及溫哥華結為友好城市。目前，他是卑詩省省長華人社區諮詢委員會成員，也是華裔加拿大人博物館董事會成員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210408/XTQYMIEEGRAZHINXCCW6XHIB6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210408%2FXTQYMIEEGRAZHINXCCW6XHIB6M%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=6af3a3c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210408%2FXTQYMIEEGRAZHINXCCW6XHIB6M%2F&h=3dc630fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210408/XTQYMIEEGRAZHINXCCW6XHIB6M/</a>"},{"pid":"2a59894473f58410e64cdb3956877bcbeaf6aaa8","tid":2479413,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T20:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY5eGHqJGMBwmyJ1A8Zw28E3kHfZwDSP2VMVHDx7g2V8u?filename=CoeT4ZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoeT4ZG.jpg&h=9c4ffe79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba4ba0b94a14f5bd4ddb87d96a986e9fbe09ac37","tid":2479413,"uid":323449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T20:16:35.000Z","msg":"蝗官"},{"pid":"55f0f5a0f7f861657220c3591e91eb11d2f2100e","tid":2479413,"uid":54344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T20:19:32.000Z","msg":"共狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIn 1993, 